  "modName": "Alchemist Rank 1 Includes Experimenter Rank 3",
  "summary": "This mod changes it so Experiment rank 3 is added when you choose the Alchemist rank 1 perk.",
  "descriptionHtml": "This mod just makes it so the highest rank of the Alchemy perk Experimenter is granted when you choose the first rank of the Alchemist perk (the very first perk in the Alchemy tree). So instead of just making potions 20% stronger, it will also make it so every ingredient effect is revealed when you eat one.\r<br />\r<br />Experimenter is a perk that makes it so more ingredient effects are revealed when you consume them. In vanilla it is a useless perk, since you can just look up all the effects outside of the game, or remember them from your previous experience. \r<br />\r<br />This is not a cheat - its just a convenience. You could look up a list to find out all the effects of the ingredients, or you could just have it all conveniently listed in-game by using this mod - much better than alt-tabbing&#33;\r<br />\r<br />UPDATES:\r<br />1.2 - Mod name and filename changed to &#39;Alchemist Rank 1 Includes Experimenter Rank 3.&#39;\r<br />\r<br />1.1 - Removed the annoying message spam about ingredient effects being learned that occurs when you consume a load of ingredients.",
